gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Warriors 132, Celtics 126
gameRecap.excerpt: Stephen Curry leads the way with 33 points (20 in the 4th and OT), six assists and six 3PM as the Warriors defeated the Celtics, 132-126, in overtime. Klay Thompson added 24 points, four rebounds and four assists in the victory, while Derrick White tallied 30 points, seven rebounds and seven 3PM for the Celtics in the losing effort. The Warriors improve to 13-14 on the season, while the Celtics fall to 20-6.
